Subject: [PATCH] Implement PDF support with auto-open and thumbnail generation

- Add PdfHandler extending ImageHandler for PDF thumbnail support
- Register PdfHandler for application/pdf MIME type
- Implement auto-open for PDF files after upload
- Add client-side auto-open in upload dialog
- Configure autoloader for PdfHandler class
- Use ImageMagick 7 syntax for PDF processing

Bug: T411157 - PDF thumbnails and auto-open functionality
Change-Id: I0d780dd679698274fb22cae5982afbcffed39673
